                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-12-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 29,
                                    1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Urge reply to your demand made in pursuance of my telegram of December
                            14.</p>
